<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  sitemap.xml: Public SEO surfaces (canonical PATH URLs).

  Path routing shipped (src/lib/routes.js), so this lists the real canonical
  paths, NOT the legacy ?view= query forms (those now client-rewrite to paths,
  which Google would otherwise read as redirect duplicates). Hand-maintained;
  update when a new public surface ships. Vercel serves /public/* as static.

  Public surfaces only. The private library, realm/map/workshop app surfaces,
  auth/account flows, and checkout are Disallow'd in robots.txt and omitted here.

  Coverage:
    /                          Home (the front door; '/' canonicalizes to /home)
    /create                    The generator
    /pricing                   Pricing
    /gallery                   Public dossier + map gallery
    /how-to                    About / how-to guide
    /compendium[?tab=…]         Reference compendium (8 sections)
-->
